generated_cypher:
MATCH (e:EC)-[:CATALYZES]->(r:Reaction) 
WITH e, COUNT(DISTINCT r) AS reaction_count 
WHERE reaction_count > 1 
RETURN DISTINCT e.id AS enzyme_id ORDER BY reaction_count DESC LIMIT 10
QAChain:
MATCH (ec:EC)-[r:CATALYZES*1..3]->(reaction:Reaction)
WHERE r IS NOT NULL
WITH ec, COUNT(DISTINCT reaction) AS num_reactions
WHERE num_reactions > 1
RETURN ec.name, ec.id, num_reactions
LIMIT 10;
QAChain_Answer: phosphoethanolamine/phosphocholine phosphatase, oleoyl-[acyl-carrier-protein] hydrolase, dodecanoyl-[acyl-carrier-protein] hydrolase, enoyl-[acyl-carrier-protein] reductase (NADH), and beta-ketoacyl-[acyl-carrier-protein] synthases I and II catalyze multiple reactions.

OPTIONAL MATCH (g)-[:BELONGS_TO]->(o:Ortholog)
WITH g, fu, ec, o
MATCH (g)<-[:CONTAINS]-(p:Pathway)
RETURN g.position AS position,
       g.name AS name,
       g.link AS link,
       g.species AS species,
       g.id AS id,
       g.symbol AS symbol,
       fu.type AS functionalUnitType,
       fu.name AS functionalUnitName,
       ec.name AS ecName,
       o.symbol AS orthologSymbol,
       p.title AS pathwayTitle
LIMIT 10;
